xed a bug where the AJAX popup would still be shown on EDD versions 2.7 or later.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Version 1.1.1, November 3, 2016</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed a bug where the popup would not be positioned in the center of the screen.</li>\n<li>Fixed a bug where the popup would re-position itself incorrectly upon scrolling the page.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Version 1.1.0, September 28,2016</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added more popup styling options</li>\n<li>Added option to reset settings</li>\n<li>Added shortcode support in popup text</li>\n<li>Added a popup preview in the settings page</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Version 1.0.1, August 1, 2016</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated author name and copyright.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Version 1.0, April 12, 2016</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:12:\"beta_version\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"beta_changelog\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"requirements\";a:0:{}s:5:\"image\";s:93:\"https://easydigitaldownloads.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/04/add-to-cart-popup-750x375.png\";s:10:\"categories\";a:4:{i:0;i:2165;i:1;i:1592;i:2;i:2166;i:3;i:2164;}s:4:\"tags\";a:0:{}s:11:\"custom_meta\";O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:8:\"basename\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"settings_tab\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"settings_section\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"license_key_option\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"943519\";O:8:\"stdClass\":17:{s:5:\"icons\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:2:\"1x\";s:109:\"https://easydigitaldownloads.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/11/edd-additional-shortcodes-880x440-128x128.png\";s:2:\"2x\";s:109:\"https://easydigitaldownloads.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/11/edd-additional-shortcodes-880x440-256x256.png\";}s:5:\"title\";s:21:\"Additional Shortcodes\";s:4:\"slug\";s:25:\"edd-additional-shortcodes\";s:7:\"version\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"updated\";s:19:\"2022-07-28 18:12:53\";s:11:\"php_version\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"wp_version\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:93:\"Adds support for additional shortcodes to show or hide content based off certain conditions\r\n\";s:2:\"id\";i:943519;s:9:\"changelo